    "rendered": "<div class=\"wpb-content-wrapper\"><p>[vc_row triangle_shape=&#8221;no&#8221;][vc_column][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<div id=\"pl-1021\" class=\"panel-layout\">\n<div id=\"pg-1021-0\" class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\">\n<div id=\"pgc-1021-0-0\" class=\"panel-grid-cell\" data-weight=\"1\">\n<p class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-headline panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"0\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\"><span style=\"font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit;\"><a href=\"http:\/\/murphlaw.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/3AttorneysImage-scaled.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-8853 alignleft\" src=\"http:\/\/murphlaw.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/3AttorneysImage-scaled.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"416\" height=\"287\" srcset=\"https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/3AttorneysImage-scaled.png 2560w, https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/3AttorneysImage-300x207.png 300w, https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/3AttorneysImage-1024x708.png 1024w, https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/3AttorneysImage-768x531.png 768w, https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/3AttorneysImage-1536x1062.png 1536w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 416px) 100vw, 416px\" \/><\/a><\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<div id=\"pg-1021-0\" class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\">\n<div id=\"pgc-1021-0-0\" class=\"panel-grid-cell\" data-weight=\"1\">\n<p class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-headline panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"0\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\"><span style=\"font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit;\">We are trial attorneys who can handle all types of complex matters. Our specialty is fighting for our clients and vigorously standing up for what&#8217;s right so that justice is served for our clients.<\/span><\/p>\n<p data-index=\"0\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\">While we always try to resolve our client&#8217;s disputes outside of court, we will not hesitate for a moment to bring a case to trial.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div id=\"pg-1021-1\" class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\">\n<div id=\"pgc-1021-1-0\" class=\"panel-grid-cell\" data-weight=\"0.5\">\n<div id=\"panel-1021-1-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"1\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\">\n<div class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\">\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n<p>Below is a list of some of the successful jury verdicts and victories we have obtained over the years. Please click the links below to find out more about our success stories:<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p id=\"panel-1021-0-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-headline panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"0\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\">\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row triangle_shape=&#8221;no&#8221;][vc_column width=&#8221;1\/2&#8243;][vc_empty_space][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<div id=\"pl-1021\" class=\"panel-layout\">\n<div id=\"pg-1021-1\" class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\">\n<div id=\"pgc-1021-1-0\" class=\"panel-grid-cell\" data-weight=\"0.5\">\n<div id=\"panel-1021-1-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"1\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\">\n<div class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\">\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n<p><span style=\"color: #003366;\"><strong>Plaintiff<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"list-style-type: none;\">\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: #003366;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #003366;\" href=\"https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/success\/client-v-confidential\/\">Client v. Confidential, et al.<\/a><\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #003366;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #003366;\" href=\"https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/success\/myers-v-meltesen\/\">Myers v. Meltesen<\/a><\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #003366;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #003366;\" href=\"http:\/\/caselaw.findlaw.com\/ca-court-of-appeal\/1655725.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Welco Electronics, Inc. v. Nicholas Mora<\/a><\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #003366;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #003366;\" href=\"\/case-results\/wolslagel-v-great-earth-international\/\">Wolslagel v. Great Earth International<\/a><\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #003366;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #003366;\" href=\"\/case-results\/blue-dolphin-ent-ltd-v-walters-et-al\/\">Blue Dolphin Ent. Ltd. v. Gary Walters, et al.<\/a><\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #003366;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #003366;\" href=\"\/case-results\/niai-v-insurance-commissioner\/\">NIAI v. Insurance Commissioner<\/a><\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #003366;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #003366;\" href=\"https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/case-results\/menke-et-al-v-lamb\/\">Menke et. al. v. Lamb<\/a><\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #003366;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #003366;\" href=\"\/case-results\/softbellys-inc-v-michael-bivens-et-al\/\">Softbelly&#8217;s, Inc. v. Michael Bivens, et al.<\/a><\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #003366;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #003366;\" href=\"https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/case-results\/sirkin-v-elliott\/\">Sirkin v. Elliott<\/a><\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #003366;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #003366;\" href=\"https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/case-results\/nanes-wasserman-v-larry-garrison\/\">Nanes &amp; Wasserman v. Larry Garrison<\/a><\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #003366;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #003366;\" href=\"https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/case-results\/studwell-inc-v-pacific-economic-dev-corp\/\">Studwell Inc. v. Pacific Economic Development Corp.<\/a><\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #003366;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #003366;\" href=\"https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/case-results\/h-h-wilson-v-ped\/\">H &amp; H Wilson v. PED<\/a><\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #003366;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #003366;\" href=\"\/case-results\/montano-v-feinstein\/\">Montano v. Feinstein<\/a><\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #003366;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #003366;\" href=\"\/case-results\/kokshanian-v-spectrum-securities-et-al\/\">Kokshanian v. Spectrum Securities, et al.<\/a><\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][vc_column width=&#8221;1\/2&#8243;][vc_empty_space][vc_column_text]<span style=\"color: #003366;\"><strong>Defense<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: #003366;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #003366;\" href=\"\/case-results\/fletcher-v-dow-chemical-company\/\">Fletcher v. Dow Chemical Company<\/a><\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #003366;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #003366;\" href=\"\/case-results\/chevron-usa-inc-v-baldeep-s-bhullar\/\">Chevron USA, Inc. v. Baldeep S. Bhullar<\/a><\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #003366;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #003366;\" href=\"\/case-results\/chevron-usa-inc-v-maureen-de-koff\/\">Chevron USA, Inc. v. Maureen de Koff<\/a><\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #003366;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #003366;\" href=\"https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/case-results\/williams-v-argueta-et-al\/\">Williams v. Argueta et. al.<\/a><\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #003366;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #003366;\" href=\"\/case-results\/singleton-v-hoag\/\">Singleton v. Hoag<\/a><\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #003366;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #003366;\" href=\"\/case-results\/clericuzio-v-demos-unlimited\/\">Clericuzio v. Demos Unlimited<\/a><\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #003366;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #003366;\" href=\"\/case-results\/dulion-v-hart\/\">Dulion v. Hart<\/a><\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #003366;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #003366;\" href=\"\/case-results\/talpis-v-wah\/\">Talpis v. Wah<\/a><\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #003366;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #003366;\" href=\"\/case-results\/carlos-v-hashim-dba-burger-king\/\">Carlos v. Hashim dba Burger King<\/a><\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #003366;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #003366;\" href=\"\/case-results\/nikou-v-khoubian\/\">Baba Nikou v. Aghajan Khoubian<\/a><\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #003366;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #003366;\" href=\"\/case-results\/rose-and-joe-esqueda\/\">Rose and Joe Esqueda<\/a><\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #003366;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #003366;\" href=\"\/case-results\/tang-v-ng\/\">Tang v. Ng<\/a><\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #003366;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #003366;\" href=\"\/case-results\/karen-zappia-v-fitovers-eyewear-et-al\/\">Karen Zappia v. Fitovers Eyewear and Paul Stables, et al.<\/a><\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #003366;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #003366;\" href=\"\/case-results\/andres-v-schmetzer\/\">Andres v. Schmetzer<\/a><\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #003366;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #003366;\" href=\"\/case-results\/joy-adv-central-tech-university\/\">Joy adv. Central Tech. University<\/a><\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #003366;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #003366;\" href=\"https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/case-results\/oscar-muro-v-john-harrington\/\">Oscar Muro v. John Harrington<\/a><\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row triangle_shape=&#8221;no&#8221;][vc_column][vc_empty_space][\/vc_column][\/vc_row]<\/p>\n<\/div>",
